    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "不分皂白来拿住",
        "四小妖",
        "孙悟空",
        "小妖甲",
        "我同妻子进京地",
        "捕役",
        "无奈只得寻死地",
        "猪悟能",
        "闻仁",
        "黑地冤枉无伸诉"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（捕役押闻仁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愁城一望无边际，"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走遍吴头并楚岐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问天何时是了期。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，闻道泉。蒙都察院老爷开恩，押我寻访娘子与百花羞下落。将及一月，可"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怜走遍天涯，哪里寻个踪迹。哎呀，天皇吓我并不曾为非作歹，平白的遭这无"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头横祸。好苦吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑地冤枉无伸诉"
        },
        {
          "character": "捕役",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也不必怨苦，好歹往前途寻问一番。若再没有，限期已满。要去回都老爷的"
        },
        {
          "character": "捕役",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥之言有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇天！我闻道泉受此无辜，怎不开眼一看哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平白飞灾来缠累，"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫天不应泪空垂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到得今生受灾危。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "披锁监押访娥眉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不然一命难免轮回。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（闻仁、捕役同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙悟空 （下山虎） 驾云迅逝，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急走如驰。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "救师岂肯迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！忽然冤气冲天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟，这冤气有些缘故。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（下山虎） 待我去探取缘由，相度事宜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥，我们去救师父要紧，别样事儿，不要管他罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（下山虎） 休戚无关同水米，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺师父方如渴慕梅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我和你在此地，哪里不知怎么着急。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟，你不晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（下山虎） 这里行程须仔细，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用多疑忌事非。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两歧好待，相逢生转机。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（捕役押闻仁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两腿疼痛步难挪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道路泥滑似滂沱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瞑目九泉待如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（闻仁撞。孙悟空、猪悟能同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那汉子为着何事，带锁披枷，寻此短见？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（捕役、闻仁同怕。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要怕。我们是大唐天子差往西天取经的圣僧徒弟。我乃孙悟空，他叫猪悟能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有什么冤情，对我们讲了。自然还你个明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位，小生闻仁。为了功名携妻上京。不期有个柏大将军呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只为元宵春灯谜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千金披卷把祸移。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空、猪悟能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可是百花羞么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空、猪悟能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你为何这等狼狈？"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父莫非知来历，"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这场冤屈世间稀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惹得捕役心带疑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三敲六问受鞭笞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那捕役将我等拿住，道我妻子，就是百花羞。被我用什么邪术，将他们来藏匿"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我同妻子进京地"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不分皂白来拿住"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙悟空"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不见妻子之时，正遇着那捕人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。可怜吓！不分皂白，将我拿到官去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁押你去访觅？"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的罪案已呈圣上，恐有含冤，批与都察院复勘。蒙那老爷审出情由，奈无实"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迹，不便回旨。赏了路费，差这位解哥押我访寻。可怜哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无踪迹，"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻两地无会期。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幸遇慈悲救残躯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无奈只得寻死地"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。我与你有缘，我二人也是为百花羞一事而来。你妻子下落，我已知道了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无奈只得寻死地"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫你雾散云开，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "重现出一轮蟾桂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父既知我妻子下落，几时才得相会？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就在目下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。你即是闻道泉么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥，事有凑巧。师父蒙百花羞放走，有书两封，一封是百花羞寄与父母，一"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "封是闻道泉之妻，寄与他丈夫的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说其中有奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥果有先见之明。服你，服你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻生请看书。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪悟能递书，闻仁看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妻吓！果然是妻子手笔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位大恩人，请上受我一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空、猪悟能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消，不消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今妻子已有了下落。并听得说什么百花羞，难道就是那柏大将军的女儿么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢天谢地。今日得遇恩人，两桩无影无踪的事情，都得明白了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要多讲。你们都随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能、闻仁、捕役同走圆场。四小妖同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小妖",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！猴公公、猪爹爹来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空打死三小妖，留小妖甲捉住。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们老妖在家么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "小妖甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不在家，到柏将军家认丈人去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这小妖也留不得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空打死小妖甲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙，都打死了。百花羞，花香洁，不知在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那里一所精致房子，一定是妖怪的内室。打进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
