        "闻仁"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（百花羞、花香洁同上。孙悟空、猪悟能同上，同赶。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花羞、花香洁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妖怪饶命吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个是百花羞？"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花羞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你便是闻道泉的妻子么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花香洁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。妖怪饶命吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好丑。你们同妖怪作了亲人，反说我们是妖怪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要胡说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位小娘子，我们不是妖怪，是唐三藏的徒弟。特来救你，不要害怕。闻生为"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了二位，受尽无限苦愁。方才投崖自尽，是我救了。带他来你们相会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花香洁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在外厢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师弟，令他夫妻相会了，随后就来。我先去救师父。拿那妖怪也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。都在我。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻生，闻道泉！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（闻仁上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来来，你妻子在这里。快来相会。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（闻仁见花香洁。〖哭相思〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，不中用的。我方便你们罢。你们紧紧的闭了眼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（百花羞、花香洁、闻仁同闭目。猪悟能呼风上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猪悟能 （尾声） 御风好似腾云气。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜从今天明月霁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双花依旧吐芳菲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
